docs.summary:
Represents the icon button that opens the hamburger menu.

> **Note:** The hamburger menu serves as an alternative to the traditional [Menu](https://www.wix.com/velo/reference/$w/menu) 
> to save space on smaller screen sizes. Its function is to toggle between an expanded and collapsed menu upon user interaction.
description: A vector image used as the button's icon.
When the users clicks the icon the hamburger menu container opens.
+ Vector images from the Media Manager: `wix:vector://v1/<vector_uri>/<filename>`
+ Vector images from the web: `http(s)://<vector image url>`
